The paper proposes a method for improving generative models by transforming a simple distribution to a data distribution in the latent space. This is a topic that is relevant to several sub-fields within computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and information theory (cs.IT). However, given that the paper focuses on improving generative models, it is most likely to belong to the cs.LG sub-category.
